body:
@sandeep-krishnamurthy turns out the installation instructions have a couple of issues.
* [-lopencv_imgcodecs](https://github.com/dmlc/mxnet/blame/master/docs/get_started/ubuntu_setup.md#L102) in the instruction should not be necessary because of [pkg-config invocation in Makefile](https://github.com/dmlc/mxnet/blob/master/Makefile#L78-L85).
* [These references to openblas](https://github.com/dmlc/mxnet/blame/master/docs/get_started/ubuntu_setup.md#L100-L101) are totally wrong because the [installation guide said to install atlas](https://github.com/dmlc/mxnet/blame/master/docs/get_started/ubuntu_setup.md#L87-L90).

@sandeep-krishnamurthy please fix both cases and send pr. Also please work with @lxn2 to make sure that in the CI the tests would actually capture this type of problems. If these don't capture problems, it means we don't need them.
